# Normalize every text file to LF in the working tree on ALL platforms. Windows
# checkouts must NOT get CRLF: the POSIX shell scripts (bootstrap.sh, the git
# hooks) require LF to run, the YAML/template/.env parsers and the marker-block
# tooling are LF-based, and the test suite asserts exact LF bytes. `text=auto`
# still auto-detects and leaves genuine binaries untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
